sub_title: PO and Naval Architect at ABB
summary:
I am a Naval Architect and Product Owner of software related to OCTOPUS (ABB Ability Marine Advisory Software). I work in the R&D department but also provide consultancy and support to clients. 
This includes general hydro-mechanics, project delivery and operations. 
I have a passion for fluid-mechanics and languages. Science and technology is something I am very interested in, as well as it´s development and influence on society.
